├── README.md                         ← Main documentation file (overview, usage, setup)
├── smart_study_planner_full.py       ← Streamlit app: study planner + calendar integration
├── forecasting.py                    ← ML script: trains model to predict completion times
├── lms_efficiency.py                 ← Data analytics script: evaluates LMS material efficiency
├── requirements.txt                  ← Python dependencies
├── rank.py                           ← Student ranking: avg mark, percentile, High/Mid/Low range
├── data/                             ← Folder for datasets
│   ├── student_assessments.csv
│   ├── student_rank_range_latest.csv
│   ├── la_dataset_lms_item_activity_by_session_fact.csv
│   ├── la_dataset_lms_item_dim.csv
│   ├── la_dataset_video_activity_by_view_fact.csv
│   ├── la_dataset_person_module_instance_outcome_fact.csv
│   └── data_dictionary.csv
│   └── outlook_calendar.ics              ← Example Outlook calendar file for demo
│   └── explore.ipynb
├── Setup/
│   ├── SETUP_ENVIRONMENT.md          ← Install Python, create venv, dependencies
│   ├── OPTION_A_LIVE_SHARE.md        ← Real-time collaboration setup
│   ├── OPTION_B_GITHUB_BRANCHES.md   ← Git branching guide
│   └── LOCAL_LLM_SETUP.md            ← Optional LLM setup
├── docs/
│   ├── PROJECT_DESCRIPTION.md        ← Detailed explanation of the system
│   ├── MODEL_TRAINING_WORKFLOW.md    ← Details on `forecasting.py`
│   ├── LMS_EFFICIENCY_ANALYSIS.md    ← Explanation of `lms_efficiency.py`
│   └── DEMO_GUIDE.md                 ← Steps to make a demo video or screenshots
├── submission_summary.md             ← Final submission write-up
└── .gitignore                        ← Ignore unnecessary or sensitive files